macro.title: Pending Home Sales Barely Budge, As Buyers Stay Cautious Despite Lower Mortgage Rates
macro.what: Homes are selling at the slowest pace for this time of year since 2019
macro.why: Rates & inflation shape discount rates and housing affordability.
macro.market: Lower rates support demand/valuations; higher rates pressure builders/REITs and slow transactions.

housing.title: 45% of Americans Say the Government Shutdown Makes Them Less Likely to Make a Major Purchase, Up From 21% in Early October
housing.what: 45% of respondents are less likely to make a major purchase overall due to the government shutdown, up from 21% in early October, according to a new Redfin survey conducted by Ipsos

housing.title: Flood-Prone America Is Seeing More People Move Out Than In for the First Time Since 2019
housing.what: An analysis of domestic migration data shows high-flood-risk counties lost nearly 30,000 more residents than they gained last year, driven largely by outflows from Miami and Houston
housing.why: Inventory and velocity drive pricing power and volume.
housing.market: Rising inventory/DOM tilts to buyers; tight supply supports prices.
